text: Interstate 210 (I-210) is the name of four Interstate Highways in the United States: * Interstate 210 (California) or the Foothill Freeway, a major eastâ€“west freeway going through the valleys north and east of Los Angeles * Interstate 210 (Louisiana), a bypass route in Lake Charles * Interstate 310 (Mississippi), a proposed freeway in Biloxi, originally proposed as Interstate 210 * Interstate 165 in Mobile, Alabama, previously designated as Interstate 210 10-2
